{"word":"ἐπιθυμέω","slug":"ἐπιθυμέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐπιϑυμέω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐπί\">ἐπί</a>, ϑυμέω</el> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ fr.\">fr.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:θυμός\">θυμός</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘have strong desire for’, <b>desire, long for <a href='B:470 13:17'>Mt 13:17</a>; <a href='B:490 15:16'>Lk 15:16</a>; <a href='B:490 16:21'>16:21</a>; <a href='B:510 20:33'>Ac 20:33</a>; <a href='B:520 7:7'>Ro 7:7</a>; <a href='B:530 10:6'>1 Cor 10:6</a>; <a href='B:550 5:17'>Gal 5:17</a>; <a href='B:610 3:1'>1 Ti 3:1</a>; <a href='B:650 6:11'>Hb 6:11</a>; <a href='B:660 4:2'>Js 4:2</a>; <a href='B:670 1:12'>1 Pt 1:12</a>; <a href='B:730 9:6'>Rv 9:6</a>.</b><el>ἐπιϑυμίᾳ ἐ.</el> eagerly desire <b><a href='B:490 22:15'>Lk 22:15</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘inordinate desire’, implying intent to acquire, <b>lust for <a href='B:470 5:28'>Mt 5:28</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐπιθήσω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐπιθυμητής\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}